<div class="card" style="max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;">
  <h2>Il mio profilo</h2>
  <div class="alert-info" style="background:#eff6ff;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:13px;color:#1e40af;">
    ℹ️ I dati dell'account admin possono essere modificati solo direttamente dal database.
  </div>
  <form>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>Nome</label>
      <input type="text" value="{{utente.name}}" disabled class="input-disabled">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>Email</label>
      <input type="email" value="{{utente.email}}" disabled class="input-disabled">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>Ruolo</label>
      <input type="text" value="Admin" disabled class="input-disabled">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>Registrato il</label>
      <input type="text" value="{{formatDate utente.created_at}}" disabled class="input-disabled">
    </div>
  </form>
</div>
